---
// Hero section for Orbit AI marketing site
---
<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-16 text-center">
  <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-xs tracking-[1px] mb-6">
    <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
    OPEN SOURCE • LOCAL-FIRST • WINDOWS OPTIMIZED
  </div>

  <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-semibold tracking-tighter leading-[0.95] mb-6">
    The lightweight<br />AI code editor<br />
    <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 via-violet-400 to-fuchsia-400">that stays local.</span>
  </h1>

  <p class="max-w-[620px] mx-auto text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-10">
    Monaco-powered desktop IDE with a powerful Groq AI assistant, integrated terminal, 
    and full local filesystem access. No cloud sync. No data exfiltration. Just fast, private development.
  </p>

  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
    <a href="https://github.com/jayakrishnanps12/orbit-ai/releases" target="_blank" class="btn-primary text-base px-8 py-3.5 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center"><span class="text-lg leading-none">↓</span> Download for Windows</a>
    
    <a href="#showcase" class="btn-secondary text-base px-7 py-3.5 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center group">See the interface live <span class="group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition">→</span></a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-8 text-sm text-zinc-500">
    <div>Electron + React</div>
    <div>Monaco Editor</div>
    <div>Groq LLMs</div>
    <div class="hidden sm:block">node-pty Terminal</div>
  </div>
</section>
